snippet.title: Shop Life Simulator - Teaser
snippet.description:
A shop life simulator and management
https://store.steampowered.com/app/3396090

From owning a small room above the store to selling exclusive products. Scratch lottery tickets to try your luck at winning big, 24/7 shop, Manage alone or with friends.
